{"tid":2174670,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK Rose敞衣只穿小可愛「辣露深溝」！　粉絲急P圖：不可以","createTime":"2020-08-26T04:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T06:53:10.000Z","uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7e815991548e8639498cd5fa8234ab05802e6816","tid":2174670,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:34:26.000Z","msg":"韓團BLACKPINK即將在28日發行和西洋小天后賽琳娜（Selena Gomez）合作的新曲回歸，陸續釋出的個人概念照也引起熱烈討論，其中成員Rose外衣敞開露出姣好身材讓人大噴鼻血，不過有些粉絲不能接受都紛紛P圖說：「不行！我來守護妳！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5097/d5097445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5097%2Fd5097445.jpg&h=878d80c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲BLACKPINK每次出新歌都吸引外界關注。（圖／翻攝自BLAKCPINK TWITTER）<br />\n<br />\n將在28日回歸的BLACKPINK從24日起依序釋出Jisoo、Jennie、Rose和Lisa的概念照，繽紛色彩又不失性感小女人的風格引起熱烈討論，呼應著炎熱夏天每個人都露出姣好身材，其中Rose則將原本是扣起來的襯衫式衣服敞開，裡面只穿著綁結小可愛露出豐滿上圍，若隱若現的深溝讓外界驚呼：「原來她身材這麼好。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5097/5097446.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5097%2F5097446.jpg&h=6eb7f018&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲Jisoo（左上）、Jennie（右上）、Rose（左下）和Lisa（右下）概念照。（圖／翻攝自BLACKPINK TWITTER）<br />\n<br />\n不過部分粉絲不希望Rose露出這麼多，紛紛P上Lisa拿鍋子遮、卡通人物拿布蓋等等圖片，就是希望能夠好好保護偶像的事業線。另外，BLACKPINK於24日也發佈了一段和賽琳娜的視訊影片，一聽到對方告白「我也是你們的粉絲，這次（合唱）對我來說是很大的夢想」難壓抑興奮情緒，這次跨國合作也吸引全世界關注。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5097/d5097447.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5097%2Fd5097447.jpg&h=c5a887bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5097/d5097448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5097%2Fd5097448.jpg&h=1c889511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲粉絲守護Rose。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5097/d5097449.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5097%2Fd5097449.jpg&h=d022958f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲BLACKPINK和賽琳娜視訊。（圖／翻攝自BLACKPINK YouTube）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dGCSeyKL5dE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdGCSeyKL5dE&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=0888d7ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dGCSeyKL5dE</a>"},{"pid":"d29c64910f850c05004d3b9fe1bcb4f7bdb01c73","tid":2174670,"uid":71632,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:38:13.000Z","msg":"A cup比盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e599b6be1f5c0b12436c2f0b4f79ddf55905ed46","tid":2174670,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:39:13.000Z","msg":"不可以只有我看到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc57c23ebec758d2665338b43d92226690c5277","tid":2174670,"uid":256952,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:40:59.000Z","msg":"D blink真係好弱智"},{"pid":"420074d4300fe811dae62052da272f71a9edc594","tid":2174670,"uid":284304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:42:37.000Z","msg":"唔遮就藝術 遮就變色情 成班弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c71e418d2e216d32945608be2e47e154681b32","tid":2174670,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:08:34.000Z","msg":"韓國粉絲仲保守過我哋......"},{"pid":"eb9562e37aae05e3b9c878843ba93716b138c011","tid":2174670,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0dc57c23ebec758d2665338b43d92226690c5277","tid":2174670,"uid":256952,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:40:59.000Z","msg":"D blink真係好弱智"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:18:46.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"c7b5462f9d9a99e102aac8856928278515738d51","tid":2174670,"uid":256952,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eb9562e37aae05e3b9c878843